about.title: About Gamers Doko
about.description: Gamers Doko is a simple website designed to help fans of Hololive Gamers track their favorite members whereabouts. It shows who is currently live, when they last streamed, and when their next stream is scheduled.
about.disclaimer: This project is not affiliated with Hololive Production. It is a fan-made project created for fun and learning purposes.
